reviewText: This movie is really funny. When I first started to watch it was on Youtube. I could not finish watching it because I just could not get into the characters. But I decided to make this purchase and watch the whole movie. Turns out I liked it so much I bought Double Dhamaal, which I am in the middle of watching now. Plus I heard there will be a sequel called Total Dhamaal which is due out in 2015. Can't wait!
